      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Hyouton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 19</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, Mob, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique functions as Jigen Ugoku no Jutsu (p172), except as above, and you can only teleport to a square containing a Hyoushou or Makyou Hyoushou barrier, or a square adjacent to one, and you cannot bring other creatures with you.</p>\n\n\n\n",
